description: Modifies the definition of an existing DataBrew project.

parameters.name: Sample
parameters.description: Represents the sample size and sampling type for DataBrew to use for interactive data analysis. Size (integer) --- The number of rows in the sample. The way in which DataBrew obtains rows from a dataset.

nested_params.name: Size
nested_params.description: The number of rows in the sample.

nested_params.name: Type
nested_params.description: The way in which DataBrew obtains rows from a dataset.

parameters.name: RoleArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role to be assumed for this request.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the project to be updated.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedDate
nested_items.description: The date and time that the project was last modified.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the project that you updated.
